headline: Can Nike Stock Double a $1,000 Investment in 5 Years?
summary: Nike’s focus on its direct-to-consumer channels helped drive greater interest in competitors' offerings.  The new CEO wants to lean on Nike’s powerful brand while reigniting product innovation.  The leader in athletic footwear and apparel has a storied history, to be sure.
